    "The combo \"exponential + Markov inequality\" is known as Chernoff's bounding technique.",
    "It is is of course very useful together with exponential inequalities like Hoeffding's inequality.",
    "with a suitable measurability condition.",
    "3 We will write ρ instead of ρ((X 1, Y 1),.",
    ", (X n, Y n)) for short."
